@AbySalto.Junior_HostAddress = http://localhost:5074

### Dohvati sve narudžbe
GET {{AbySalto.Junior_HostAddress}}/api/restaurant/orders
Accept: application/json

### Dohvati sve narudžbe sortirane prema izračunatom ukupnom iznosu računa
GET {{AbySalto.Junior_HostAddress}}/api/restaurant/orders?sortByTotal=true
Accept: application/json

### Dohvati narudžbu po ID-u
GET {{AbySalto.Junior_HostAddress}}/api/restaurant/orders/1
Accept: application/json

### Kreiraj novu narudžbu
POST {{AbySalto.Junior_HostAddress}}/api/restaurant/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Test Korisnik",
  "paymentMethod": "Cash",
  "deliveryAddress": "Testna ulica 1, Zagreb",
  "contactNumber": "0911234567",
  "note": "Bez alergena",
  "currency": "EUR",
  "items": [
    {
      "name": "Pizza",
      "quantity": 2,
      "price": 8.50
    }
  ]
}

### Promijeni status narudžbe
PATCH {{AbySalto.Junior_HostAddress}}/api/restaurant/orders/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": 1
}